Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.71,0:01:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:63716,64717}{\i1}Versailles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.75,0:01:07.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:65759,67720}{\i1}We've finally reached Versailles!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:21.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:75352,81984}{\i1}Isabelle's group escaped in a balloon\Nfrom Paris which was still under siege.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.98,0:01:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:81984,88032}{\i1}After some adventures, they finally\Narrived at their destination, Versailles.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.65,0:01:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:88657,92369}Isabelle, look!\NYour parents came to pick you up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.87,0:01:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:95873,97958}Mother! Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:99918,100836}Isabelle!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.04,0:01:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101045,102755}– Isabelle!\N– I'm coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.17,0:01:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103172,104882}Mother…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.71,0:01:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:105716,106634}Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.13,0:01:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110137,111555}Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.55,0:01:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111555,112806}I'm so glad you're safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.43,0:01:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113432,116477}It's because I was with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.18,0:01:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:117186,119063}Oh, it's you, Victor.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:119688,122483}I am indebted for\Ntaking care of our little Isabelle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.10,0:02:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:123108,126612}Yes, we wouldn't be alive\Nwithout Mr. Victor.Right, Jean?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.61,0:02:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:126612,130074}Huh? But I also… I also…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.07,0:02:12.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:130074,132493}Never mind.\NThere is no talking to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133786,137039}Welcome to Versailles,\NGeneral Gambetta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.03,0:02:19.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:137039,139375}The hardest is yet to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.37,0:02:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:139375,142670}We must gather as many people\Nas possible, and do it fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.67,0:02:25.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142670,145506}Then we need to go\Nand save the city of Paris.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.13,0:02:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:146131,151011}Do you think that Paris\Ncan hold out in the meantime?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.97,0:02:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:151970,157976}The citizens of Paris are burning\Nwith anger and want to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.97,0:02:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157976,160979}Your son is among them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:160979,165109}I fully trust Andréa.
