Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:03.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1440049,1443886}I received a secret letter\Nfrom my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.88,0:24:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1443886,1447223}She has some friends in London\Nwho can help us win Paris back,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.22,0:24:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1447223,1450559}and she asks me\Nto contact them.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.89,0:24:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1450893,1454146}What… What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.60,0:24:18.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1454605,1458192}London is so far away…\NAnd I'm a girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.19,0:24:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1458192,1460861}I have to watch out for Thiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.86,0:24:23.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1460861,1463322}Next time on "Isabelle from Paris":
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.32,0:24:27.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1463322,1467243}"The Birth of a Beautiful Swordslady".\NPlease look forward to it.
